.\" Man page for appicon
.TH APPICON 1 "July 2026" "appicon" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
appicon \- resolve desktop and brand icons to local file paths
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B appicon
\fIcommand\fR [\fIoptions\fR] [\fIargs\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B appicon
looks up an application or brand icon and prints a local filesystem path.
Consumers such as Waybar, Rofi, and scripts can use the path without embedding
remote download logic.
.PP
Resolve order: existing path, FreeDesktop icon theme / .desktop (including
Flatpak, Snap, and Steam heuristics), then configured logo sources (SVGL and/or
local packs via sources.json). A miss exits with status 1.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B resolve [\-\-json] [\-\-offline] [\-\-local] [\-\-format svg|png] [\-\-size N] [\-\-theme dark|light] \fIquery\fR
Resolve \fIquery\fR and print the absolute path (or JSON with \-\-json).
When a daemon socket is present, dial it unless \-\-local or APPICON_NO_DAEMON is set.
.TP
.B prefetch \fIquery\fR...
Warm the cache for one or more queries.
.TP
.B cache path|clear|stats|prune
Inspect or manage the on-disk cache under $XDG_CACHE_HOME/appicon.
.TP
.B daemon [\-\-socket \fIpath\fR]
Run the optional unix-socket resolve daemon (or under systemd socket activation).
.TP
.B mcp
Run a stdio MCP server for coding agents (tools: resolve, prefetch, cache_*, version).
.TP
.B completion bash|zsh|fish
Print a shell completion script to stdout.
.TP
.B man
Print this man page (troff) to stdout.
.TP
.B version
Print the version string.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B XDG_CACHE_HOME
Cache root parent (default ~/.cache). Assets live in $XDG_CACHE_HOME/appicon.
.TP
.B XDG_CONFIG_HOME
Config parent (default ~/.config). Reads appicon/overrides.json and sources.json.
.TP
.B APPICON_THEME
Default dark|light preference when \-\-theme is omitted.
.TP
.B APPICON_ICON_THEME
Override FreeDesktop icon theme name.
.TP
.B APPICON_SOCKET
Override daemon socket path (default $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/appicon.sock).
.TP
.B APPICON_NO_DAEMON
When set, resolve never dials the daemon socket.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/appicon/overrides.json
Query remaps (e.g. WM class to catalog name).
.TP
.I $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/appicon/sources.json
Ordered logo sources: svgl, dir packs, http-index.
.TP
.I $XDG_CACHE_HOME/appicon/
Downloaded SVGs, http-index assets, and rasterized PNGs.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Icon not found (resolve miss).
.TP
.B 2
Other error.
.SH SEE ALSO
Documentation: https://github.com/bolens/appicon
